Vyjayanthimala

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For the garland in Hindu mythology, see Vaijayanti.


Vyjayanthimala Bali



Vyjayanthimala at Esha Deol's wedding at ISKCON temple in Bangalore in 2012



